Package server

Class Invocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.Invocation
  • public class Invocation
extends java.lang.Object
    Invocation class implements calling of methods during runtime. Objects of all controller classes are created before server execution starts. These objects are stored so that their methods can be called as Invocations during handling of an HTTP Request.
